  "title": "Warehouse Assistant",
  "description": "<p>📦 <strong>Hiring: Warehouse Assistant</strong><br /><br /><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><p><p>Assist in receiving, sorting, and storing goods<br />Picking and packing orders for delivery<br />Maintain cleanliness and organization of the warehouse<br />Help with stock inventory and reporting</p></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p><p>Able to follow instructions and work in a team<br />Physically fit and able to lift moderate weights<br />Responsible and reliable<br />No experience required (training provided)<br /><br />📍 <strong>Location: </strong>Yishun<br />🕙 <strong>Working Hours: </strong>5.5 days per week<br /><br />Interested parties:<br />Click ''<strong>APPLY</strong>'' or<br />Send your resume to <em><strong>admin@psmanpower.com </strong></em>with the subject line: “<em><strong>NEFT3136 Application</strong></em>”</p><p>Only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.<br />By applying for this role, you consent to PS Manpower Pte Ltd PDPA<br />Data collected is strictly used for recruitment purposes only.</p></p>",
